---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="APFS-RS Local Handoff">
  <h1>Local Handoff</h1>
  <p>First run the cargoless checks, then run Rust/Cargo checks on a local machine.</p>
  <pre><code>python3 tools/cargoless_smoke_suite.py
cargo fmt --all -- --check
cargo test --workspace
cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets --all-features -- -D warnings</code></pre>
</Base>
